        {
            "block_label": "text",
            "block_content": "To increase the diversity and script coverage of the data we also include data for additional lower-resource languages. For these languages, we opt to use human-generated parallel data instead. This data comes from the SMOL (Caswell et al., 2025) and GATITOS (Jones et al., 2023) datasets. SMOL covers 123 languages and GATITOS covers 170.",
